Objective 1: ✅ Done
Project leaders can create/manage project profiles and activities; approval flow in place.
Objective 2: ⚠️ Partially done
Beneficiaries are created & stored; join/approve/decline works. Missing: strong admin/leader UI + export for managing beneficiary lists.
Objective 3 (email blast via Nodemailer): ❌ Not done
Nodemailer is set up and many event emails send, but there is no dedicated “email blast” feature (select audience + compose + send to many).
Objective 4 (client satisfaction survey): ⚠️ Partially done
Survey collection per activity is implemented. Missing: organizer dashboards/analytics and exports.
Objective 5 (attendance tracking): ✅ Done
Attendance per activity (registered/present/absent) works, with UI guards, in‑app notifications, and now email notifications to participants.